1
00:00:00,000 --> 00:00:05,000
Welcome to A.I. Rural Finance, an intelligent credit decisioning platform for rural entrepreneurs.

2
00:00:05,000 --> 00:00:13,000
First, we test the built-in accessibility speaker, reading matching scheme benefits aloud in local languages.

3
00:00:13,000 --> 00:00:21,000
Next, we take the interactive Credit Booster Quiz. Answering successfully boosts our credit score by plus five percent.

4
00:00:21,000 --> 00:00:32,000
By opening the UPI QR Code modal and triggering a simulated client payment, the backend updates our cash flow ledger dynamically.

5
00:00:32,000 --> 00:00:43,000
Navigating to the Loans page, we see our micro-credit history and claim the emergency interest-free weather relief overdraft.

6
00:00:43,000 --> 00:00:50,000
Finally, we slide the Credit Score Simulator to see how growing revenue and lower expenses immediately increase borrowing limits.
